  <div class="post-block post">
    <link itemprop="mainEntityOfPage" href="https://ojbk8.github.io/Debian-Ubuntu-Nginx-Certbot-Let’s-Encrypt-SSL">

    <span hidden itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
